These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, western, martial-arts, family
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, subway, snowmobile, quad-bike
1. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
5. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the snowmobile##2
6. the person watching family movies is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | drama     | martial-arts | western |
| Transport     | trike     | snowmobile | quad-bike  | subway      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, soul, funk, reggae
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, taxi, bike, van
1. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far left or far right##3
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the person driving the van##1
4. the person driving the van is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the fan of funk is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | soul    | reggae     | funk  |
| Transport     | scooter    | bike | taxi | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, d&b, hip-hop
4 different pets are kept: horse, guinea-pig, goldfish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
2. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the fan of metal##3
5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | trance   | d&b   | metal  | hip-hop |
| Pet           | guinea-pig | hedgehog | goldfish | horse  |

