.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, photography, skydiving, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, french, canadian, chinese
1. the chinese is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
2. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person who's hobby is chess and the canadian##2
3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##3
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
5. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the indonesian is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Hobby         | photography | chess | reading | skydiving  |
| Nationality   | french  | indonesian   | chinese  | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, juice, mirinda
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, traveling, gardening, writing
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is traveling##3
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the person who's hobby is writing is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | milk    | tea   | juice | mirinda    |
| Hobby      | traveling | card-games | gardening       | writing |

