3. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the van and the person drinking lemonade##2
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | lemonade | milk | cola | tea |
| Transport   | subway | scooter  | van    | motorbike  |

