.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: puzzles, reading, rock-climbing, collecting
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, western, disaster, crime
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person watching western movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
4. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is reading##1
6. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby         | collecting | rock-climbing | puzzles | reading   |
| Movie-Genre   | western | disaster | zombie      | crime |

