.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, guinea-pig, pony, bird
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, swimming, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the owner of the bird##1
4. the owner of the cat is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is climbing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | cat | guinea-pig   | pony      | bird      |
| Sport   | swimming     | lacrosse | climbing | skateboarding |

