.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-11::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, video-games, rock-climbing, fishing
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, jet-ski, scooter, helicopter
1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person driving the scooter##3
5. the person driving the helicopter is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person driving the scooter is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby       | cooking | rock-climbing | fishing    | video-games      |
| Transport   | scooter       | helicopter       | jet-ski | trike |

