1. the pakistani is on the far right##1
2. the australian is the australian##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the pakistani##3
5. the indonesian is on the left or right of the chinese##3
6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left or right of the chinese##3
7. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
