2. the videographer is on the right of the scientist##1
3. the person eating cucumber is on the left of the dancer##1
4. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating eggplant is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Food   | cucumber  | apricot | cherry  | eggplant      |
| Job    | doctor | dancer | scientist | videographer |

