4. the fan of pop is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
5. the fan of rock is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
6. the fan of rock is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
7. the fan of pop is on the left or right of the fan of r&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography | hiking | woodworking | drawing |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | r&b       | pop   | rock      |

