.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, biathlon, climbing, soccer
1. the person who's sport is climbing is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person who's sport is climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | juice     | coffee     | sprite          | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | rowing | biathlon | soccer | climbing  |

 